<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Dear Raffaella,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Thank you so much for your continued patience and un=
derstanding while we work through your request.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We truly appreciate the opportunity to gather all th=
e necessary information for you. Unfortunately, due to limited resourcing, =
we&#8217;re still working through the correspondence and aren&#8217;t quite=
 finished yet. We&#8217;re really sorry for the delay
 and kindly ask for one more week to complete the request.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">In the meantime, we&#8217;ve uploaded everything we&=
#8217;ve been able to obtain so far. You can access the documents via the l=
ink provided. The newly gathered information is stored in a folder titled
<b>&#8220;Request 3.&#8221;</b><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><a href=3D"https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-s5e9753b3=
b30d40a9a6c1b57e9a5b6630">https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-s5e9753b3b30d40a9=
a6c1b57e9a5b6630</a><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We look forward to your response and apologise for t=
he inconvenience.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Warm regards<o:p></o:p></p>
